eventText: Shantanu has asked Dominik to provide more information on About page and Support page.
Sharyu has said all 6 statics images are approved, and can be send to Web production team.
Shantanu sends a doubt to Dominik, as in ADA app both Support and feedback are same. Asks for any other suggestions.
Client sent us the Google Play developer console invitation @14Feb. Sambhaji accepted the invitation and replied back to Dominik.
All 4 guidelines are now on CMS. Cardiac Chamber Quantification by Echocardiography in Adults  guideline is on CMS.
Sambhaji informs Dominik about the keystore and password. Also sends screenshot of developer console.
First testflight version is sent to Frank and Dominik.
Dominik suggests changes in the About page, @20Feb, 5:35AM.
Dominik sends the keystore, alias name and password for Android app. Sambhaji forwarded the keystore to Neville.
Shantanu and Soumya worked overtime on Sunday, 25Feb.
Both iOS and Android apps are uploaded on testflight.
Programmers inform Dominik that direct external linking from the home screen icons will be a change request. This feature will not be integrated in first technical version.
Sambhaji contacts Dominik that we haven't received invitation for iTunes Connect, Amazon S3 and Google Analytics.
Shantanu has asked for email addresses of testers to speed up testing process.
ASEcho app is sent on testflight to Frank, Dominik
Dominik says to take 3 April as deadline for now.
Change request received from Dominik
Dominik choose plan A to add all the future guidelines on home screen. Clicking on icon will lead to TOC with one entry and coming soon HTML page.
Mariona says that Cecilia will do the task of updating the POC.
Dominik says that, Client is okay on 22 May.
The app to be updated is now confirmed by client and information forwarded by Dominik.
Mariona is asking for editorial input for making changes in the design draft till tomorrow morning.
Cecilia has updated and sent the updated DD on @3Apr.
The DD is revised by the production team and sent the feedback to Frank, Cecilia.
Cecilia makes the changes and resends the DD for review.
Shantanu sends the app requirements to Dominik.
